# Basic

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:bpf, path: ".."}
])
```

## Opening & Loading

```elixir
object = BPF.Object.open_file!("syscall_counter.o")
```

```elixir
BPF.Object.load!(object)
```

```elixir
link = BPF.Program.attach!(object.programs["do_sys_exit"])
```

```elixir
for i <- 0..256 do
  BPF.Map.lookup_elem!(object.maps["syscall_counts"], i)
end
```
